text: The Gang's All Here is a 1943 American musical movie directed by Busby Berkeley and starring Alice Faye, Carmen Miranda, Benny Goodman, Phil Baker, Eugene Pallette, Charlotte Greenwood, Edward Everett Horton. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1944. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * The Gang's All Here at NNDB * * Category:1943 musical movies Category:1940s American musical movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Busby Berkeley
